---
title: Peri Peri-Honey Pork & Creamy Slaw with Garlic & Corn Rice
description: There’s nothing to this dish, it’s as easy as tossing creamy mayonnaise through a colour slaw and serving on top of a
fragrant garlic rice. Next the pork, jazz it up with a mouth-watering peri-peri sauce and there you have it, dig in!
